	<description>
		<p>You're playing against the AI in a chess match. 
The AI has vast computational resources, but you have hacks. 
Use your hacks to win!</p>
	</description>
	<branding>
		<color type="primary" scheme_preference="light">#fabc5f</color>
		<color type="primary" scheme_preference="dark">#593807</color>
