	<releases>
		<release version="1.03" date="2024-10-03">
			<description>
				<p>Added experimental support for mobile devices.</p>
				<p>Updated the application icon.</p>
				<p>Other minor changes.</p>
			</description>
		</release>
		<release version="1.02" date="2023-05-23">
			<description>
				<p>The opponent's pawns can now be captured en passant even if the pawns didn't start on the second rank.</p>
				<p>After completing the game, the AI's starting piece configuration can now be selected.</p>
				<p>The music no longer briefly plays when launching the game, if the music volume had previously been muted.</p>
				<p>Audio files now use ogg format (instead of wav) to reduce file sizes.</p>
				<p>Other minor changes.</p>
			</description>
		</release>
